concatstr.c, exh.c: Include stdlib.h and string.h.

	* concatstr.c, exh.c: Include stdlib.h and string.h.
	* delaycase.c, eqstr.c, memmove.c, printbuffer.c,
	printevent.c, sendbuffer.c, waitbuffer.c: Include string.h.
